## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/xtensaconstantpoolvalue">XtensaConstantPoolValue</a> - <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/xtensa">Xtensa</a> specific constantpool value.

This is used to represent PC-relative displacement between the address of the load instruction and the constant being loaded.

Definition at line 48 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/target/lib/target/xtensa/xtensaconstantpoolvalue-h">XtensaConstantPoolValue.h</a>.
